ApplicationInsightsAPI provides an interface to enable mocking the applicationinsights.ApplicationInsights service client's API operation, paginators, and waiters. This make unit testing your code that calls out to the SDK's service client's calls easier.

The best way to use this interface is so the SDK's service client's calls can be stubbed out for unit testing your code with the SDK without needing to inject custom request handlers into the SDK's request pipeline.

}
